OL,3,CZombie knife amnesty scheme begins as
OL,4,Cpeople urged to hand in weapons
OL,6,FAn amnesty scheme for those in
OL,7,Fpossession of zombie-style knives and
OL,8,Fmachetes is starting today in England
OL,9,Fand Wales ahead of a ban on the
OL,10,Fweapons.
OL,12,FPeople are being urged to hand over
OL,13,Fthe weapons safely and legally at
OL,14,Fdesignated police stations before a
OL,15,Fnew ban comes into force.
OL,17,FFrom September 24, it will be illegal
OL,18,Fto own zombie-style knives and
OL,19,Fmachetes.
