OL,3,CZombie knife amnesty scheme begins as
OL,4,Cpeople urged to hand in weapons
OL,6,FThe blades will be added to the list
OL,7,Fof dangerous prohibited items already
OL,8,Fbanned, including butterfly knives,
OL,9,FSamurai swords and push daggers.
OL,11,FThe amnesty scheme will run for four
OL,12,Fweeks ` between August 26 and
OL,13,FSeptember 23 ` in police stations
OL,14,Facross England and Wales.
OL,16,FPeople in possession of the weapons
OL,17,Fare being encouraged to contact their
OL,18,Fdesignated police station first to get
OL,19,Fadvice on how to package them up and
OL,20,Fbring them into the station.
