OL,4,Cpeople urged to hand in weapons
OL,6,FPeople can also anonymously dispose of
OL,7,Fweapons using surrender bins, by
OL,8,Fcontacting their local police force,
OL,9,Fthe council or an anti-knife crime
OL,10,Fcharity to find out about alternative
OL,11,Foptions in their area.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThere will be no "repercussions" for
OL,19,Fthose surrendering these blades
OL,20,Fsafely, according to the Home Office.
