OL,3,CZombie knife amnesty scheme begins as
OL,4,Cpeople urged to hand in weapons
OL,6,FThe government said anyone found with
OL,7,Fa zombie-style knife or a machete
OL,8,Ffollowing the ban faces time behind
OL,9,Fbars.
OL,11,FThe scheme is part of the government's
OL,12,Fpledge to halve knife crime in a
OL,13,Fdecade.
OL,15,FEarlier this month, Policing Minister
OL,16,FDame Diana Johnson said that there "is
OL,17,Fno legitimate need" to have a weapon
OL,18,Fof that kind in homes or on the
OL,19,Fstreets.
