OL,3,CZombie knife amnesty scheme begins as
OL,4,Cpeople urged to hand in weapons
OL,6,FShe said: "Too many people have access
OL,7,Fto weapons that can lead to
OL,8,Fdevastating, life-changing
OL,9,Fconsequences.
OL,11,F"It is absolutely crucial that members
OL,12,Fof the public come forward and safely
OL,13,Fhand in these weapons. We are offering
OL,14,Fpeople the chance to do the right
OL,15,Fthing ` to help make our streets
OL,16,Fsafer, prevent further loss of life
OL,17,Fand save so many futures.
